title: The Digger's Daughter: An Australian Saga
description: Jane is a tough, pioneering Australian woman. She has lived a long and eventful life, but it is nearing its end. Her family were amongst the earliest in Melbourne and Victoria. She has a story to tell of the 1850s goldrush, but is determined to keep her background secret from her family. Her nurse, Mary, has stories from the Great War. Will they help each other come to terms with what they each have hidden in the past?
author: Rosemary Noble
